Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Notice:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This DVD is a special gift from Shogakukan to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When watching this DVD, please turn on\Nthe lights and sit away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow the Vanished Diamond!\NConan & Heiji vs. Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:30.01,Title,,0,0,0,,FOLLOW THE VANISHED DIAMOND!\NCONAN & HEIJI VS. KID!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you like for dinner, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I really want to make sukiyaki, but my dad hasn't had much work lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have to save up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Today we have a discount on beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good, I'll make croquettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have 150... I mean 100 grams, please?{Will you give me 150 grams? Well, make it 100.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And eggs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, who's this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he lives with us.{we're taking care of him.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s illegitimate son, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, Auntie.{Stop playing around, Auntie.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:09.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, with 20 grams on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potatoes, onions, cabbage, tomatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, this is on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who would have thought that Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} had a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in everyone! Cheap fish!{need to edit this to make the flashback flow better}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can have\Nthat for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look as energetic as ever, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.{Always so lively, Ran.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's always shopped like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take these clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect, now I can make miso soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, she's just as popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.32,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}That was "Cooking with Okino Yoko"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:23.24,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Today's guest was the great detective, Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Well then, until next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, how many times does he have to watch this video before he gets tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This tape must be worn out by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares? We don't have any customers anyway...{Don't meddle where you're not asked, if only I had clients...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that, Dad? Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a package for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get that, but from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Dad! It's not anything indecent, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What are you talking about? I need it for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are you going upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's suspicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? He must be hiding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't "huh" me, do you have the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll record it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,Private Number{NUMBER NOT AVAILABLE}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blackmail phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the phone number didn't show up, we can't return the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the man didn't mention\Nwho he was trying to call, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called here by accident, our number must be similar to the one he was looking for.{the number he meant to call must be similar to ours.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, we should hurry up and call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget about it, what you guys just told me doesn't hold much water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no proof that there's been a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably was just a debt collector calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I've arranged to play mahjong.{Well, I promised to play mahjong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to what Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's true that there's no proof that it's a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:48.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if there's a kidnapping, we don't have time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't "huh" me, do you have the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.55,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That voice... I've heard it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:06.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.12,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:13.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd say I've heard that voice recently, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:19.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute, the only voices I've heard recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...{My goodness...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.05,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cheap fish!{Fish at a great price! / Fish is cheap!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You look as energetic as ever, Ran{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-chan{\r\be10}.{Always so lively, Ran.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're having a discount on beef today.{change original line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:32.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's not Mouri{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s illegitimate son, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cabbage, tomatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:38.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who would have thought that Ran{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-chan{\r\be10} had a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could they be...?!{What if...?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because we don't use pesticides.{It's because ours is pesticide-free.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:50.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...  It's a little similar, but it's not that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{Thanks for your business.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where was it? Where did I hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, did I catch you at a good time?{Hello, sorry to bother you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Moriwaki from TM Trading. Is the {General Manager}chief in?{The Japanese name, TM Shoji, is a reference to TMS. Also the man is speaking with a Kansai accent which makes Conan react.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo... I mean Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make me come all the way from Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be very important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A call from a blackmailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says the man's voice sounded exactly like yours, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.{He says the blackmailer's voice reminds him a lot of yours, Heiji.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard that voice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he spoke in a strange way{the way he spoke was different},\Nso I didn't recognize it.{I couldn't be sure.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the reason why we called you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To find out who the man was trying to call,\Nby having me place calls as the blackmailer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To every single number similar to that of the detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know from their reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, as I expected from Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I can tell it's your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already compiled a list of\Nphone numbers, so we'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, without further ado...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you leave the rest to me and the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then I'll be preparing{cook/make?} dinner.\NIf you need help with anything, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preparing dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a very homely detective agency, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time for small talk. Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.44,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? This is Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey 'tis me... It's me.{ore-ya/ore-da}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.78,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I must have the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I've got the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.74,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? This is Iwatsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What more do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You filthy thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:45.04,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've handed over the ten million yen and\Nhaven't spoken with the police, as we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.67,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You shouldn't have any more business with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the sound of it, the man has already paid and closed the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he called me a filthy thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly did he mean by "thief"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we are, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, you're the boy who's always with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've come to visit Iwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's Iwatsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're investigating a fraud case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewelry theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Iwatsume is a rare name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So after looking him up on the internet we found out he's a jewelry appraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that there probably was a jewel robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're not sure how blackmail is related.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's meet this Iwatsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:10:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't robberies handled by the third division?\NYou're from the second...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm already here... and I can't ignore it if they tell me about a jewel robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see something just fly by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably a giant flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do the police want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember hearing this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you catch the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What criminal? I'm talking about the jewel thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, we've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the details,\Nwe need the victim's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day before yesterday, 100 million yen was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:07.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is not the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't have such a strange accent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of the Osaka{Kansai} dialect?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Naniwa high school detective, Hattori Heiji!{Naniwa is the old name for Osaka}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer! What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, the fact is that a hundred million yen\Nworth of jewelry has been stolen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it hasn't been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a moment ago you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see, so that's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jewel was stolen, but he offered to return it if you paid him 10 million yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Why would I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing is, you had already sold it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if it cost you 10 million yen,\Nit would still be worth it to get the jewel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I get it right, Iwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't arrest the criminal now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may strike again, maybe a second or third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, just like Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I have a lot of bad memories because of that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I won't forgive you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Speaking of which, I wonder if he'll be coming for this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute, this jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This thief isn't very greedy, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't pay attention to him.{No, don't mind him.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a jewel worth 100 million yen, he only got ten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I would have asked for at least half of what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely strange to ask for only ten percent of what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the jewel you got back is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a case of fraud, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you admit it now, Iwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, do you know anything about the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, although I gave him money, we didn't meet in person. I only heard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the phone? Did you record it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like the old man and the girl are asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, you don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to re-enact the call we had, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Since it's not the thief's real voice,\Nwe can't use it as evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that should help us find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do ya have the money ready?{Have ya prepared the money?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not like that! "Have you got the money ready?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not, and that's precisely why Iwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} figured you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, one more time.\N"Do you have the money ready?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do ya have the money prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like that! Why can't you say it like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can I do? I'm an Osaka man from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, at this rate, you'll never get these lines right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what if I can't say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You wouldn't speak the Osaka dialect well either}If you were asked to speak in the Osaka dialect, you wouldn't be able to, it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the same! I can at least\Nspeak the Osaka dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can? {Now that I recall,}I do recall that you once explained your deductions in a very strange Osaka dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, using my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The voice-changing bowtie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll only take one try with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think of that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what they call having it right under your nose, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori, you can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:08.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please listen to the voice of the suspect in the theft of 100 million yen worth of jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.32,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Do you have money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.42,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Don't "huh" me, do you have the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.32,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:25.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}If you recognize this voice, please call the special phone line of the Metropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s voice, right?\NYour standard Japanese accent is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, 'tis quite useful for a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised they didn't realize it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Inspector Nakamori realized that it was Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}'s voice right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even knowing that, he dared to have it broadcast on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy seems to have some guts as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The influence of TV is huge,\Nthere'll soon be an avalanche of calls...{the calls will start pouring in...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'tis me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Heiji! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voice was just on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in a weird Tokyo dialect, but it was definitely your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your family in so much financial trouble\Nthat you'd have to steal jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! How can you expect me to steal jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone calls really are pouring in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kudo, about that\N"good morning" you heard on the call...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember where you heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, although I've thought about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it sounded more muffled than the man's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Okino Yoko's Special Figurine Alarm Clock"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the package Uncle recieved yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you want this?{What is this for?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Limited to members only\NAlarm clock of Okino Yoko in an apron\NSerial number
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute, Okino Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is well made, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.95,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's morning, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's that voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, that's the voice from the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a specially made alarm clock that's only available to members of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, how much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it matter how much it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two... Two thousand yen.{$17.5}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand yen...{$175}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand yen?\NI'm barely making ends meet right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you spend that kind of money on a toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you were hiding it from us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only two hundred of them were made,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I wanted one so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only two hundred were made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can get the names of people from the fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the criminal probably bought the clock and set the time wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when he was talking to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:22.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:33.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The next day, thanks to the fan club's list and\Na call from a viewer, the jewel thief was identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you come any closer, I'll throw this into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His voice really does sound like mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.74,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning! It's morning, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.78,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning! It's morning, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{Kid} probably was after the jewel too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he saw us going investigating before he sent the warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he was up to date on the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was no flying squirrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations, little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And to you too, detective of the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After him! Don't let Kid get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what they call having it snatched away from right under your nose.{That's what they call coming up empty-handed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I came all the way from Osaka for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an idiot... I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:32.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Whimsical Kaito Kid\NReturns Hundred Million Yen Jewel to Its Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, one more! Pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! From now on, no smoking, and you're only allowed one beer a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Such a waste of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a very homely detective agency, isn't it?
